ed from the VAE representation using samples derived from the **hu35ksuba** platform only. These quantities summarize within-class geometric structure and separation between normal and tumor states in the learned latent space.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n\n|Measure             | Normal|  Tumor|  Delta|\n|:-------------------|------:|------:|------:|\n|Participation ratio |  2.162|  2.431|  0.269|\n|Eigenvalue entropy  |  0.906|  1.199|  0.293|\n|Anisotropy          |  0.614|  0.581| -0.034|\n|Radius              | 14.985| 25.331| 10.347|\n|Centroid distance   | 25.847|     NA|     NA|\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n:::\n",
